Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（発砲音）\N（怨霊）ぐあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（通行人Ｂ）キャーッ！　ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（通行人Ｃ）うわあ～！
